plot_Gaussian.py: three Gaussian functions
movie1.py:  primary animation example
movie1_mpl.py: version of movie1.py in native Matplotlib syntax
plot_ascii.py: demo of the ASCII plotter (for inclusion in verbatim text)
hat.py: various vectorization techniques for a hat function
heatwave*.py: plotting the heat waves in the summarizing example of ch 5
difficulties.py: illustrate a few challenging functions to plot

mpl_pylab_examples.py: matplotlib pylab examples
mpl_pyplot_examples.py: matplotlib pyplot examples
easyviz_examples.py: easyviz examples corresponding to the mpl_*.py files

See the examples directory of the SciTools source code distribution
for a lot of different examples of tuning plots via Easyviz.
(code.google.com/p/scitools)




